Step 1:
Download Apache Kafka
Download the Kafka binaries from Apache Kafka.
Extract the downloaded Kafka package to a directory.

Step 2:
Start Zookeeper
Kafka requires Zookeeper to run. Navigate to the Kafka directory and start Zookeeper:

bash
    bin/zookeeper-server-start.sh config/zookeeper.properties

Step 3:
Start Kafka Server
Once Zookeeper is running, start the Kafka broker:

bash
    bin/kafka-server-start.sh config/server.properties

Step 4:
Create Kafka Topic
Create the "sendEmail" topic for the email service:

bash
    bin/kafka-topics.sh --create --topic sendEmail --bootstrap-server localhost:9092 --partitions 1 --replication-factor 1


Step 5:
Verify the Topic
To verify that the topic was created:

bash
    bin/kafka-topics.sh --list --bootstrap-server localhost:9092